Package Shared

Class Assignment

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shared.Assignment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Assignment
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Provides data fields and methods to create a Java data-type, representing a Assignment in a Learning Platform Java application. The overall purpose of this class is to store information to display and send between the client and server.
    Since:
    March 5, 2018
    Version:
    1.0
